<div class="NavFrame collapsed" style="border:none; padding:0;">
<div class="NavHead" style="background:papayawhip; text-align: center; padding-left:0.4em;">Internationals</div>
<div class="NavContent" style="padding:0.2em 0 0.4em; text-align:center;"><a href="/wiki/Communist_League" title="Communist League">Communist League</a><br />
