<td style="padding:0.3em 0.4em 0.3em; font-weight:bold; border-top:1px solid #aaa; border-bottom:1px solid #aaa; text-align:center;"><b><a href="/wiki/Portal:Communism" title="Portal:Communism">Communism Portal</a></b></td>
